{"tid":1059583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民航處宣佈13/3 18:00起禁飛波音B737 MAX型號客機","createTime":"2019-03-13T08:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T03:32:04.000Z","uid":26602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f08760dcd4b420cf2b6be779e0c5f61369289e1","tid":1059583,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"埃塞俄比亞航空一架載有149名乘客的航班周日（10日）發生空難，全機人罹難。事後全球多個國家禁止屬出事航班同一機型的波音B737 MAX型號客機飛越領空，本港民航處亦宣佈自今日傍晚6時起，暫時禁止所有波音B737 MAX型號飛機進出或飛越香港。<br />\n<br />\n民航處稱根據事件的最新情況，決定暫時禁止所有波音B737 MAX型號飛機進出或飛越香港，禁令今日下午6時起生效，直至另行通知。又指有關臨時禁制僅為預防措施，以確保航空安全和保障公眾。<br />\n<br />\n因應較早前印度的香料航空（SpiceJet）和俄羅斯的Globus Airlines仍使用B737 MAX型號飛機，在香港國際機場營運往返香港和目的地的航班。民航處已就有關臨時禁制的安排聯絡該兩間航空公司，兩間公司均表示全力配合，並以其他機種繼續提供服務，以盡量減少對乘客的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190313/59363805\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F59363805&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=75dde3ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F59363805&h=9f7d1047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190313/59363805</a><br />\n<br />\n香港都跟大隊bam B737 Max<br />\n幾時到FAA出手全球force ground<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddab5bc25323be90718680805a74b967a7a98ce","tid":1059583,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"美國點會ban自己友，除非係美國炒返鑊先有機"},{"pid":"faab465dd7b6b9b9655600d8e978c3c8ac29a15e","tid":1059583,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eddab5bc25323be90718680805a74b967a7a98ce","tid":1059583,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"美國點會ban自己友，除非係美國炒返鑊先有機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9ca3a73a7bd33bd339fb03ea82e40ed41fcc22","tid":1059583,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eddab5bc25323be90718680805a74b967a7a98ce","tid":1059583,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"美國點會ban自己友，除非係美國炒返鑊先有機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}